            "maestro-layer": "L7 — Agent Ecosystem"
          }
        },
        {
          "ruleId": "tachi/stride/elevation-of-privilege",
          "message": {
            "text": "M8 Privilege-Gain: Exported Debug Activity Bypassing Auth Boundary: WellnessBankDebugActivity retained in production release build with android:exported=\"true\"; accessible via adb shell am start; no BuildConfig.DEBUG runtime guard; no Play Integrity attestation gate; privileged-action flow connects directly to WellnessBank Android Client bypassing the standard authentication boundary.",
            "markdown": "Strip WellnessBankDebugActivity from release builds via Android Gradle build-flavor configuration. Implement build-time validation asserting no *Debug* components ship in release artifacts. Integrate Play Integrity API on all privileged-action paths. References: OWASP M8:2024; CWE-732; OWASP MASVS-PLATFORM; OWASP MASTG-RESILIENCE"
          },
          "level": "error",
          "locations": [
            {
              "physicalLocation": {
                "artifactLocation": {
                  "uri": "examples/mobile-banking-app/architecture.md"
                },
                "region": {
                  "startLine": 1
                }
              },
              "logicalLocation": {
                "name": "WellnessBankDebugActivity",
                "fullyQualifiedName": "Device Zone/WellnessBankDebugActivity",
                "kind": "process"
              }
            }
          ],
          "partialFingerprints": {
            "findingId/v1": "E-1"
          },
          "properties": {
            "security-severity": "8.5",
            "cvss-base-score": "10.0",
            "cvss-vector": "CVSS:3.1/AV:L/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:C/C:H/I:H/A:H",
            "exploitability": "9.5",
            "scalability": "8.0",
            "reachability": "4.5",
            "composite-weights": "0.35/0.30/0.15/0.20",
            "severity-band": "High",
            "risk-owner": "Unassigned",
            "remediation-sla": "7d",
            "risk-disposition": "Mitigate",
            "review-date": "2026-05-06",
            "maestro-layer": "Unclassified"
          }
        },
        {
          "ruleId": "tachi/stride/elevation-of-privilege",
          "message": {
            "text": "Unauthorized Money Transfer via Intent Hijacking and Privilege Escalation: Exported MoneyTransferActivity with no android:permission allows any installed app to invoke the money-movement flow. Combined with missing re-authentication at Activity entry, a malicious co-installed app escalates from unprivileged-app context to authenticated-banking-session context, executing fund transfers without any user interaction.",
            "markdown": "Set android:exported=\"false\" or enforce android:permission with signature protection level. Require re-authentication at every money-movement Activity entry. Implement per-Intent caller verification (getCallingPackage() with package allowlist). References: OWASP M8:2024; OWASP M4:2024; CWE-862; CWE-732"
          },
          "level": "error",
          "locations": [
            {
              "physicalLocation": {
                "artifactLocation": {
                  "uri": "examples/mobile-banking-app/architecture.md"
                },
                "region": {
                  "startLine": 1
                }
              },
              "logicalLocation": {
                "name": "MoneyTransferActivity",
                "fullyQualifiedName": "Device Zone/MoneyTransferActivity",
                "kind": "process"
              }
            }
          ],
          "partialFingerprints": {
            "findingId/v1": "E-2"
          },
          "properties": {
            "security-severity": "8.3",
            "cvss-base-score": "9.3",
            "cvss-vector": "CVSS:3.1/AV:L/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:C/C:H/I:H/A:N",
            "exploitability": "9.5",
            "scalability": "8.5",
            "reachability": "4.5",
            "composite-weights": "0.35/0.30/0.15/0.20",
            "severity-band": "High",
            "risk-owner": "Unassigned",
            "remediation-sla": "7d",
            "risk-disposition": "Mitigate",
            "review-date": "2026-05-06",
            "maestro-layer": "Unclassified"
          }
        },
        {
          "ruleId": "tachi/stride/tampering",
          "message": {
            "text": "Mobile IPC Input Validation (M4) — Intent Hijacking into Money Movement: Exported MoneyTransferActivity with android:exported=\"true\" and no android:permission accepts Intent extras (recipient_account, amount) from any installed app or ADB shell directly into the money-movement flow without re-authentication, schema validation, or per-Intent caller verification.",
            "markdown": "Set android:exported=\"false\" unless cross-app invocation is required. If exported, declare android:permission with signature protection level. Validate all Intent extras against a strict schema; require re-authentication on every money-movement invocation. References: OWASP M4:2024; OWASP MASTG-CODE; OWASP MASVS-PLATFORM; CWE-20; CWE-862"
          },
          "level": "error",
          "locations": [
            {
              "physicalLocation": {
                "artifactLocation": {
                  "uri": "examples/mobile-banking-app/architecture.md"
                },
                "region": {
