          "message": {
            "text": "Insecure Mobile Data Storage (M9) — Local Database: Unencrypted SQLite database with allowBackup=\"true\" exposes full transaction history and account snapshots to Google Drive cloud backup. Attacker compromising the user's Google account can recover complete financial history without bypassing device authentication.",
            "markdown": "Encrypt WellnessBankLocalDB via SQLCipher with Keystore-bound key. Set allowBackup=\"false\" or define explicit Android 12+ backup rules excluding the database. Apply database TTL eviction policy. References: OWASP M9:2024; OWASP MASTG-STORAGE; OWASP MASVS-STORAGE; CWE-311; CWE-312"
