          "ruleId": "tachi/stride/spoofing",
          "message": {
            "text": "Missing Token Binding on Backend Session: The backend API accepts HTTPS bearer tokens without certificate pinning on the client side, enabling token replay from intercepted sessions. No device-binding means a captured token is replayable from any device.",
            "markdown": "Implement token binding (DPoP or mTLS certificate-bound tokens) on the backend API. Verify device attestation (Play Integrity) server-side on transaction-confirmation calls. References: OWASP A07:2021; CWE-287"
